  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I might mention it, on the tape, that my stories are many, and hanging--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why we were going already outside of the ghetto, and hiding, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we heard that in this town they killed 5,000, in this town they killed all the population, that suddenly, 2,000 people were taken.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were digging graves. 200 people, 12,000 people-- the men-- were taken, digging graves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, the, the city was full of rumors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Suddenly, there's a lot of Lithuanians in town, and there are a lot of others.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think Lithuanians were on the [INAUDIBLE] that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] is full.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was-- oh, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's why it's already-- that's why father went the one side, my sisters went in another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother and the aunts stayed in the same place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But just to finish up the story with [? stamps ?] there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So finally, Ranger-- but the point was, when he came in, this young soldier-- because it's so unusual, that's why I think it's worthwhile mentioning it-- those other two soldiers told me to sit down behind the cabinet.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when somebody goes in, they couldn't see me immediately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They would see just a table.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was sitting behind that closet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they told me that Ranger is in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he came in, and I started-- and he said to me-- and I also saw a lieutenant there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the lieutenant, two [? gendarmes ?] came and they wanted for [? many ?] people to, for this, I presume for the slaughter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I did hear enough to hear him say [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] For those kind of things, I do not have men.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
